EN: This bank offers current deposit services.

ZH: 活期利率通常会比定期利率低。
EN: Current interest rates are usually lower than fixed deposit rates.

ZH: 你可以随时取出活期存款中的金额。
EN: You can withdraw money from your current account at any time.

ZH: 活期存款没有期限限制。
EN: There is no term limit for current deposits.

